ProjectTitle: Development of processes and techniques for the microfabrication of painless vaccine injection patches
InitialFeedbackHistory:
28/06/2022
Very nice and detailed tables for your data and documentation. You however don't have to list your own presentations and manuscripts in a DMP. 
Please note that KU Leuven also has a gitlab that may be handy for work: https://gitlab.kuleuven.be/. Data sharing may be easier using a repository such as KU Leuven RDR: www.kuleuven.be/rdm/en/rdr or domain specific repositories recommended by the journals where you plan to submit your manuscripts
label: good with suggestions
